      ],
      description: ["Ever had some leftover gas/liquid in a machine that you can't remove because you can't pull it out?", "The Gauge Dropper can remove gas/liquid from any Mekanism machines input or output slot, and either insert it into another input or output slot, or void it.", "Simply click the Gas/Liquid with the Gauge Dropper in the machine interface (like you're about to Drag-n'-drop it) to extract it, and right click to insert it (given it is in the correct input/output slot).", "You can also Shift-Click with it on a gas/liquid to void all its stored contents in that slot, or shift-right click with it to void its own contents."],
