  subtitle: ["Mekanism is a very technical mod that includes everything somebody could ever need.", "Simple machine setups for those new to the whole Tech side, with easy ore processing, lots of misc items and low RF generation (~60rf/t), and really complicated machine setups for the maximum profit, like complicated ore processing (upto x5 processing), machine automation and really high RF generation (200k+ rf/t).", "Mekanism is a big mod, so the quests will be split into 2 parts. This is Part 1, that includes the Basic and Advanced parts of Mekanism.", "", "Disclaimer: You are expected to know how to look up recipes in JEI (Just Enough Items).", "", "", "Authored by Discomanco."],
